The Chronicle  Lizzy Nekhoma and Maita Zizhou online reporters DESPITE numerous warnings and educational campaigns over the years scores of Zimbabweans drown every year, mainly due to irresponsible behaviour.  The simple warning DO NOT ATTEMPT TO CROSS FLOODED RIVERS goes unheeded.  These videos have been taken from social media showing downright recklessness that leads to loss of life.  Please DO NOT GAMBLE WITH YOUR LIVES!